text: Maddy Gough (born 8 June 1999) is an Australian swimmer. She competed in the women's 1500 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships held in Gwangju, South Korea. She finished in 5th place in the final. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female freestyle swimmers
